# <type>(<scope>): <short summary, imperative, no period>
#
# Types:   feat | fix | refactor | chore | docs | test | perf | style | ci | revert
# Scopes:  feature slice (library, playback, catalog, metadata, ...)
#          OR layer (domain, application, adapters, platform)
#          OR cross-cutting (mobile, api, docs, deps, tooling, claude-md)
#
# Body (why > what):
# Explain *why* this change is needed. The diff shows what changed.
# Reference specs/ADRs/solutions when relevant: see docs/specs/<name>/spec.md
#
# Footer (optional):
# Refs: #issue, ADR-NNNN
# BREAKING CHANGE: <description>
#
# Do NOT include AI co-author lines (Co-Authored-By: Claude/AI/Anthropic).
# The commit-msg hook will strip them automatically.
